'''Akarere ka Çankaya''' (soma "cankaya", izina mu [[giturukiya]] : ''Çankaya ilçesi'' ) ni akarere kari mu [[Intara y’Ankara|ntara y’Ankara]] y’igihugu cya [[Turukiya]]. Akarere ka Çankaya ni kamwe mu turere 16 tugize Intara y’Ankara. Akarere gatuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri 785.330  (abagabo 383.654 n’abagore 401.676)<ref>[http://report.tuik.gov.tr/reports/rwservlet?adnksdb2=&report=idari_yapi_2008.RDF&p_il1=6&p_yil=2008&desformat=html&ENVID=adnksdb2Env  TÜİK]</ref> , batuye kubuso bwa km² 267,61  .

== Izina ==
Iryo zina ryakomotse ku magambo 2 yo m’ururimi rw’igiturukiya ariyo («'''çan'''» 'bell' na «'''kaya'''» 'ibuye').

== Akarere gahana imbibe ==
Gahana imbibi na:
:Mu majyaruguru :  Akarere k’[[Etimesgut]], Akarere ka [[Yenimahalle]] n’Akarere k’[[Altındağ]]
:Mu burasirazuba : Akarere ka [[Mamak]]
:Mu majyepfo : Akarere ka [[Bala]] n’Akarere ka [[Gölbaşı]]
:Mu burengerazuba : Akarere ka [[Yenimahalle]]

